<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;input
                type="datetime-local"&gt; </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">元素的</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> datetime-local
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">类型创建让用户便捷输入日期和时间的输入控件，包括“年”、“月”、“日”，以及“时”和“分</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>

                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span

                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                                style="color:white"><strong>说明</strong></span></span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td
                style="border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:1.7388in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">max</span></span>
                </p>
            </td>
            <td
                style="border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:6.6888in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">接受的最晚日期和时间的值。如果</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> value </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的值晚于这一时间戳，则该元素不会通过约束验证。如果</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> max </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">属性的值不是遵循</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">格式的有效字符串，则该元素没有最大值。</span></span></p>
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">该属性指定的值必须晚于或等于</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> min </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">属性的值。</span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td
                style="background-color:#e7e6e6; border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:1.7388in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">min</span></span>
                </p>
            </td>
            <td
                style="background-color:#e7e6e6; border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:6.7187in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">接受的最早日期和时间的值。如果早于这一时间戳，则该元素不会通过约束验证。如果</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> min </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">属性的值不是遵循</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">格式的有效字符串，则该元素没有最小值。</span></span></p>
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">该属性指定的值必须早于或等于</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> max </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">属性的值。</span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td
                style="border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:1.7388in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">step</span></span>
                </p>
            </td>
            <td
                style="border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:6.7187in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">step
                        </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">属性是一个数字，用于指定值调整的步长；或使用特殊值</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> any</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。该属性的描述如下：仅能使用基础的调整步长（若</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> min </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">已指定，则从其开始；否则使用</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> value</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">；若两者均未提供，则为某一适当的默认值）。</span></span>
                </p>
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">字符串值</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> any </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">表示没有步长约束，任何的值均可使用（除了其它的约束，如：</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">min </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> max</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）。</span></span></p>
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><strong>注</strong></span></span></p>
                <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
                    <li><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">当用户输入的数据不符合配置的步长限制时，用户代理可能会将其四舍五入到最近的有效值，当有两个差值相等的选项时，优先选择大于当前值的数值。</span></span>
                    </li>
                    <li><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对于</span></span><span
                            style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">
                                datetime-local </span></span><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">输入控件，</span></span><span
                            style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">step
                            </span></span><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">值的单位是秒，最小分度为</span></span><span
                            style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">
                                1/1000</span></span><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">（因为底层的数值以毫秒为单位）。默认的</span></span><span
                            style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> step
                            </span></span><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">值为</span></span><span
                            style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">
                                60</span></span><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，表示</span></span><span
                            style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 60
                            </span></span><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">秒（或一分钟、</span></span><span
                            style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">60000
                            </span></span><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">毫秒）</span></span></li>
                </ul>
            </td>
